		</div>
	</div>
	
	<div id="confirm-order-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-[200] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cat-pine/80 backdrop-blur-md"></div>
		
		<div class="relative bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 max-w-sm w-full shadow-2xl border-2 border-cat-yellow text-center animate-text-entrance">
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-cat-pine italic mb-4">On y est ! 🐾</h3>
			
			<div id="confirm-details" class="text-sm text-cat-pine/70 mb-6 space-y-2">
				</div>

			<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
				<button id="final-whatsapp-btn" class="w-full bg-cat-yellow text-cat-pine py-4 rounded-full font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-lg">
					Envoyer sur WhatsApp
				</button>
				
				<button id="no-whatsapp-btn" class="w-full border-2 border-cat-pine/10 text-cat-pine/60 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase hover:bg-cat-pine/5 transition-all">
					Je n'ai pas WhatsApp
				</button>
				
				<button id="cancel-confirm-btn" class="text-xs text-red-400 font-bold uppercase mt-2 hover:underline">
					Modifier ma commande
				</button>
			</div>

			<div id="sms-fallback-msg" class="hidden mt-6 p-5 bg-cat-teal/10 rounded-[2rem] border border-cat-teal/20 animate-text-entrance">
				<p class="text-[11px] text-cat-teal font-bold leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Pas de soucis ! Appelez ou envoyez un SMS directement au <span class="text-cat-pine underline font-black">07 62 35 13 91</span> pour confirmer votre commande. 🐾
				</p>
				
				<button id="confirm-alt-btn" class="w-full bg-cat-teal text-white py-3 rounded-full font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-md">
					J'ai envoyé mon message
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="profile-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-[110] hidden">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cat-pine/60 backdrop-blur-sm" id="close-profile-overlay"></div>
		<div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-full max-w-md bg-white shadow-2xl p-8 flex flex-col">
			<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-10">
				<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-cat-pine italic">Mon espace Pho-rever</h3>
				<button id="close-profile-btn" class="text-2xl hover:rotate-90 transition-transform">✕</button>
			</div>

			<div id="profile-login" class="space-y-6">
				<p class="text-cat-pine/70 italic text-sm">Entrez votre numéro pour consulter vos points de fidélité et vos cadeaux.</p>
				<input type="tel" id="lookup-phone" placeholder="06 12 34 56 78" class="w-full border-2 border-cat-pine/10 rounded-xl p-4 outline-none focus:border-cat-teal transition-all" />
				<button id="check-loyalty" class="w-full bg-cat-teal text-white py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg">Voir mes points</button>
			</div>

			<div id="profile-stats" class="hidden space-y-8">
				<div class="bg-cat-yellow/20 p-6 rounded-3xl text-center border-2 border-cat-yellow">
					<p class="text-cat-pine font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">Ma Cagnotte</p>
					<div class="text-5xl font-black text-cat-pine"><span id="user-points">0</span> <span class="text-xl">pts</span></div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="space-y-4 bg-cat-pine/[0.03] p-6 rounded-[2rem] border border-cat-pine/5">
					<div class="flex justify-between items-end">
						<div>
							<p class="text-[11px] font-black italic text-cat-pine uppercase tracking-widest">1 point collecté tous les 10€ dépensés</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col items-end">
							<span class="text-[12px] font-black text-cat-teal italic uppercase">🎁 10€ offerts</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="w-full bg-cat-pine/10 h-3 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-inner">
						<div id="points-bar" class="bg-cat-teal h-full transition-all duration-700" style="width: 30%"></div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="flex justify-between items-center px-1">
						<p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-black tracking-widest text-cat-pine/50">
							Plus que <span id="points-needed" class="text-cat-teal text-xs">7</span> points avant votre bon d'achat !
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<button id="change-phone-btn" class="mt-8 text-xs font-bold text-cat-teal uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer">
					← Consulter un autre compte
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="cookie-banner" class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 w-full z-[100] hidden animate-text-entrance">
		<div class="bg-cat-pine text-cat-wood p-4 md:p-6 rounded-t-[2rem] shadow-[0_-10px_25px_-5px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] border-t border-cat-yellow/20 backdrop-blur-md">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
				
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
					<div class="bg-cat-yellow p-2 rounded-xl text-cat-pine shrink-0 hidden sm:block">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10 4 4 0 0 1-5-5 4 4 0 0 1-5-5"></path><path d="M8.5 8.5v.01"></path><path d="M16 15.5v.01"></path><path d="M12 12v.01"></path><path d="M11 17v.01"></path><path d="M7 14v.01"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-center md:text-left">
						<h4 class="font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-cat-yellow inline-block mr-2">Pause Cookie ?</h4>
						<p class="text-xs leading-relaxed opacity-80 italic inline md:block">
							On utilise uniquement des cookies techniques pour que votre panier et vos points de fidélité restent à jour lorsque vous actualisez le site ! Pas de pub, promis ! 🐾
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex gap-3 shrink-0">
					<button id="accept-cookies" class="bg-cat-yellow text-cat-pine px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-[10px] uppercase hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-md">D'accord</button>
					<button id="decline-cookies" class="text-cat-wood/60 hover:text-cat-wood px-4 py-2 font-bold text-[10px] uppercase transition-all underline underline-offset-4">Continuer sans accepter</button>
					<button id="more-cookies" class="border border-cat-wood/30 px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-[10px] uppercase hover:bg-cat-wood/10 transition-all">En savoir plus</button>
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

</Layout>